---
import Base from "../layouts/Base.astro";
---

<Base
  title="Terms of Use — Giftly Lists"
  description="Giftly Lists terms of use."
>
  <style>
    nav {
      display: flex;
      justify-content: space-between;
      align-items: center;
      padding: 24px 40px;
      border-bottom: 1px solid #1f1f1f;
    }
    .logo {
      font-size: 18px;
      font-weight: 700;
    }
    .back {
      font-size: 14px;
      color: #d90701;
    }
    .content {
      max-width: 680px;
      margin: 0 auto;
      padding: 80px 40px;
    }
    h1 {
      font-size: 48px;
      font-weight: 800;
      letter-spacing: -0.03em;
      margin-bottom: 16px;
    }
    .updated {
      color: #444;
      font-size: 13px;
      margin-bottom: 64px;
    }
    h2 {
      font-size: 20px;
      font-weight: 700;
      margin-top: 48px;
      margin-bottom: 12px;
    }
    p {
      color: #888;
      font-size: 15px;
      line-height: 1.7;
      margin-bottom: 16px;
    }
    ul {
      color: #888;
      font-size: 15px;
      line-height: 1.7;
      padding-left: 24px;
      margin-bottom: 16px;
    }
    li {
      margin-bottom: 8px;
    }
    a {
      color: #d90701;
    }
    @media (max-width: 600px) {
      nav {
        padding: 20px 24px;
      }
      .content {
        padding: 48px 24px;
      }
      h1 {
        font-size: 36px;
      }
    }
  </style>

  <nav>
    <span class="logo">🎁 Giftly Lists</span>
    <a href="/" class="back">← Back</a>
  </nav>

  <div class="content">
    <h1>Terms of Use</h1>
    <p class="updated">Last updated: June 2026</p>

    <p>
      These Terms of Use govern your use of the Giftly Lists mobile application
      ("App") operated by Red Surge Technology ("we", "our", or "us"). By
      downloading or using the App, you agree to these terms.
    </p>

    <h2>Use of the App</h2>
    <p>
      Giftly Lists is a gift wishlist sharing app. You may use the App to create
      gift lists, add items, and share lists with others. You are responsible
      for all activity that occurs under your account.
    </p>
    <ul>
      <li>You must be at least 13 years old to use the App.</li>
      <li>You may not use the App for any unlawful purpose.</li>
      <li>
        You may not attempt to gain unauthorized access to any part of the App
        or its infrastructure.
      </li>
    </ul>

    <h2>Accounts</h2>
    <p>
      You may sign in using Google or Apple. You are responsible for maintaining
      the security of your account. We are not liable for any loss resulting
      from unauthorized use of your account.
    </p>

    <h2>Subscriptions</h2>
    <p>
      Giftly Lists offers an optional auto-renewable subscription called <strong
        >Giftly Pro</strong
      > at <strong>$1.99/month</strong>. Giftly Pro unlocks up to 25 gift lists
      and removes ads.
    </p>
    <ul>
      <li>
        Payment is charged to your Apple ID account at confirmation of purchase.
      </li>
      <li>
        Subscriptions automatically renew monthly unless cancelled at least 24
        hours before the end of the current period.
      </li>
      <li>
        You can manage or cancel your subscription at any time in your device's
        App Store settings.
      </li>
      <li>No refunds are provided for partial subscription periods.</li>
    </ul>
    <p>
      By subscribing, you also agree to Apple's standard <a
        href="https://www.apple.com/legal/internet-services/itunes/dev/stdeula/"
        target="_blank"
        >Licensed Application End User License Agreement (EULA)</a
      >.
    </p>

    <h2>User Content</h2>
    <p>
      You retain ownership of the content you create in the App (list titles,
      item names, links). By using the App, you grant us a limited license to
      store and display your content solely for the purpose of providing the
      service.
    </p>

    <h2>Termination</h2>
    <p>
      We reserve the right to suspend or terminate your account if you violate
      these terms. You may delete your account at any time by emailing <a
        href="mailto:support@giftlylists.com">support@giftlylists.com</a
      >.
    </p>

    <h2>Disclaimer of Warranties</h2>
    <p>
      The App is provided "as is" without warranties of any kind. We do not
      guarantee that the App will be uninterrupted, error-free, or free of
      viruses or other harmful components.
    </p>

    <h2>Limitation of Liability</h2>
    <p>
      To the fullest extent permitted by law, Red Surge Technology shall not be
      liable for any indirect, incidental, special, or consequential damages
      arising out of your use of the App.
    </p>

    <h2>Changes to These Terms</h2>
    <p>
      We may update these terms from time to time. Continued use of the App
      after changes constitutes acceptance of the new terms.
    </p>

    <h2>Contact Us</h2>
    <p>
      If you have questions about these terms, email us at <a
        href="mailto:support@giftlylists.com">support@giftlylists.com</a
      >.
    </p>
  </div>
</Base>
